							I'm playing it some.<br />
Some of my old WoW raiding buddies are really into it, and plays it alot.<br />
Personally I don't like the graphical style of the game, but it's not too buggy, and you can play it reasonably well without having to pay anything - At least it feels like I contribute about as much as the ones that have shelled out some cash for bonuses.<br />
<br />
Maybe over time it'll become much more of an unfair battle, but currently it doesn't seem bad.<br />
